I GOT A THEORY. So he is running from he's shadow, ok that's simple. May be his shadow are his insecurities, his "to do" things, his past, his problems and all that things, and he is like telling to us "don't let me shine"/"don't let me fly" because he thinks that if the shadow catch him, that will take him appart of us so we have to save him(?), Also he's running to be free (obviously) bc rn he's not, so that's what the lyrics says:"I wanna be..." In the future, and when he's gonna be free, without the shadow, he will feel like he can do all that he said on the lyrics. And with the shadow, he doesn't feel him self, he has to be what society wants him to be.
I thought this like ten minutes before writing this and when I wrote this, I forgot what I thought. Believe me, when I thought it, it heared better.... I'm sorry if nobody understood something, I'm so bad explaining myself...
